Text: How long does it take to get an orgasm?
Message JSON: {"userId":"8e64c942-8aa3-40ce-91a6-425e15048155","text":"How long does it take to get an orgasm?"}

Text: An orgasm (aka, coming) happens when your body releases tension that builds up when masturbating, having sex, or being intimate with someone else. It's often intense and really good feeling. Both guys and girls can orgasm. When orgasming, someone might notice that their heart beats fast, and their face gets flushed. Orgasms can be tricky, and it's totally normal to not be able to have one, or for it to take awhile.
